---
title: Indexer State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OFF

    OFF --> ASSIST_INTAKING : SuperStructure sets ASSIST_INTAKING
    ASSIST_INTAKING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    OFF --> INDEXING : SuperStructure sets INDEXING
    INDEXING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    OFF --> REVERSING : SuperStructure sets REVERSING
    REVERSING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    ASSIST_INTAKING --> INDEXING : SuperStructure sets INDEXING
    INDEXING --> ASSIST_INTAKING : SuperStructure sets ASSIST_INTAKING
    ASSIST_INTAKING --> REVERSING : SuperStructure sets REVERSING
    INDEXING --> REVERSING : SuperStructure sets REVERSING
    REVERSING --> INDEXING : SuperStructure sets INDEXING
    REVERSING --> ASSIST_INTAKING : SuperStructure sets ASSIST_INTAKING

    note right of OFF
        Duty cycle = 0.0
        Motor stopped
    end note

    note right of ASSIST_INTAKING
        Duty cycle = -0.15
        Reverse assist during intake
        Prevents jamming
    end note

    note right of INDEXING
        Duty cycle = 0.75
        Forward feeding balls
    end note

    note right of REVERSING
        Duty cycle = -0.35
        Clearing jams
    end note
